premise_source_doc_sentence: The DePauw is a tabloid-sized newspaper published most Wednesdays of the school year by the DePauw University Board of Control of Student Publications .
The tabloid-sized newspaper was first published in October 1980 .
The tabloid-sized newspaper , with a circulation of 2,000 , is published roughly 25 times during the academic year from its office in the basement of Burton Hall .
